{"tid":1197873,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"暴力事件 就算自焚 政府都未必回應你","createTime":"2019-06-10T05:40:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T23:03:35.000Z","uid":152262,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1dccae3e8d7f10fe8b9c874f0d5529e9d034e6ce","tid":1197873,"uid":152262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T05:40:17.000Z","msg":"我好感動 仍然有班香港人願意企出黎<br />\n為自己 為下一代 為香港爭取<br />\n但你暴力衝擊 最終都係自己身心受傷<br />\n失敗只會帶比你更大嘅無力感<br />\n<br />\n總有人話香港<br />\n仲未有流血事件<br />\n仲未有人死 政府係唔會理<br />\n<br />\n但藏人係中國不斷都有自焚事件<br />\n的確可以喚起國際嘅關注<br />\n但中共有啲咩回應？有咩改變？<br />\n你有你繼續自焚，我有我繼續打壓<br />\n就算國際嘅聲音都阻止唔到<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">係中共眼中人命一啲都唔值錢！</span><br />\n<br />\n對於香港最值錢一定係經濟 姐係錢！<br />\n只有罷工罷市 先會逼到政府表態<br />\n中國佬都好需要香港洗乾淨啲錢<br />\n<br />\n但香港好多人都手停口停<br />\n打工嘅好似同份工結左婚<br />\n做老細嘅又怕得罪到人<br />\n有幾多人會出黎罷工啊。。。"},{"pid":"3c6bdd70d7335b7c1dd496f23f82b58377ca6235","tid":1197873,"uid":152262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T05:49:50.000Z","msg":"The city is dying <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8873883441da323e557c82ebdc4cc1b42ad9df4f","tid":1197873,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:03:42.000Z","msg":"呢個社會就係咁等於我哋喺老細心目中價值係零一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc88d99e565a35f7955d87038a46c4e22091474c","tid":1197873,"uid":152262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8873883441da323e557c82ebdc4cc1b42ad9df4f","tid":1197873,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:03:42.000Z","msg":"呢個社會就係咁等於我哋喺老細心目中價值係零一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:10:56.000Z","msg":"弘<img src=\"/assets/faces/